Package: deepin-font-manager
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libdeepin-font-manager( =${binary:Version})
Replaces: deepin-font-installer
Conflicts: deepin-font-installer
Description: Deepin Font Manager binary
 Font manager is a powerful font management tool. With Font Manager, you are not only able to search, install, enable, disable and delete fonts among others, but also preview fonts by inputting texts and setting the text size. It supports fonts in ttf, ttc and otf formats.

Package: libdeepin-font-manager
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Multi-Arch: same
Description: Deepin Font Manager library
 This package contains the shared libraries.

Package: libdeepin-font-manager-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libdeepin-font-manager( =${binary:Version})
Description: Deepin Font Manager Devel library
 This package contains the header files and static libraries
 of libdeepin-font-manager
